La Ley - Retour (2014)




Retour is the album that reintroduces multi-Grammy winning band LA LEY back to their millions of fans throughout the world. Retour features the brand new studio track "OLVIDAR" and also compiles the band's biggest hits from 1989 up to 2004, including some of the unforgettable performances from their live MTV Unplugged release which includes the hits "Mentira," "Intenta Amar" and "El Duelo (feat Ely Guerra)". Seventeen tracks are available on Retour.
